    "AICC also surpasses RefinedWeb and FineWeb on key benchmarks.",
    "We publicly release WebMainBench, MinerU-HTML, and AICC, demonstrating that HTML extraction is a critical, often underestimated component of web corpus construction.",
    "IntroductionThe remarkable capabilities of modern large language models (LLMs) are built upon massive-scale pretraining on diverse text corpora [5,28,29,10].",
    "As models scale to hundreds of billions of parameters and training extends to trillions of tokens, the quality and quantity of pretraining data have become critical determinants of model performance [14].",
